//App MicroServices

// Auth Service
	|-> Login
	|-> Register

// Permission 
	|-> Add Permission
	|-> Edit Permission
	|-> Delete Permission For User
	|-> Give Permission


// Users Service 
	|-> Add User
	|-> Edit User
	|-> Delete User
	|-> Update User
	|-> Ban User


// Costumer Service 
	|-> Create Order
	|-> Confirme Order
	|-> Cancel Order
	|-> Track Order
	|-> Report For Something wrong
	|-> Chat  
	|-> Rate Delivery Service
	|-> Rate Product 

//Restorant Service
	|-> Accept Order
	|-> Open Shop
	|-> Close Shop
	|-> Menu Edit (Add/Update/Delete)
	|-> Chat

//Courier Service
	|-> Accept Order
	|-> Cancel Order
	|-> Start delivery
	|-> Complete delivery

//Delivery Integration
	|-> Integrator



//Domains
	|-> Auth
	|-> Costumer
	|-> Delivery
	|-> Order
	|-> Payment
	|-> Notifications
	|-> Rate
	|-> Users
	|-> Product


//Datebase Tables
	|-> analytics        
	|-> auth             
	|-> feedbacks        
	|-> files            
	|-> jobs             
	|-> notifications    
	|-> orders           
	|-> orders_couriers  
	|-> orders_tracking  
	|-> products         
	|-> users            
	|-> users_orders


//Technologies
